{"tid":1354023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[嚴肅]元朗集會一定一定唔可以玩火","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:28:54.000Z","uid":16217,"like":88,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e70d77373cc971a57b24b5fd5108e0bb1e59851c","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:16:28.000Z","msg":"眼見好多手足 甚至posts係到推燒村 我好擔心<br />\n我非常支持感謝勇武打到呢個地步 但有好多打手係到分化呢到手足吹風吹到只要勇武就支持到底 希望大家怒火中保持思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武既義士都係持有犧牲小我 完成大我既高尚情操<br />\n但係大家記住大我係對抗港共 而對抗港共除左勇氣 仲需要智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎到呢個階段我地聚焦政黑警共勾結 得到既群眾力量更大 更加正名,符合我地既抗爭宣言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n胡亂推post 大數量正評真係有可能令火遮眼既勇士放火 到時&rdquo;大我&rdquo;係會越黎越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果都有賣當日人馬係來自各方各路 當日鄉黑只係南邊圍村果到扎馬 你滅果條村都唔能夠所謂起哂班黑社會出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之和理非 組自衛隊 被動地行使公民逮捕權<br />\n我可以用身體對抗鄉黑 至多毆鬥罪 但再煽動放火就好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 最後 防止放火唔係和理非同勇武切割 而係唔好比仇恨掩蓋 追求短暫快感 放棄更大群眾利益</span></span>"},{"pid":"9bf59a06d6acc462b18ef904b996faebbe1407db","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f72eeb26cd75d83aaa3f50ebcde206948a89507","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:23:27.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1560eaf88d6c6560f90d3f54f8e00499070608","tid":1354023,"uid":262589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8cef82f1ec6eadaec616070418227c4516f1c16a","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"建議admin del燒村post 免遭口實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b7ff179675063b10c68e6aa7d4fd5e460b761d","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"建議admin del燒村post 免遭口實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45252e42520e24ad0472f660d5b2cb51917d1f69","tid":1354023,"uid":41245,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"其實放火搞到消防<br />\n火又唔係成日玩就唔好玩啦<br />\n一陣搞埋自己友<br />\n我支持大家做任何嘢<br />\n但係有把握唔會殺錯人先好"},{"pid":"e3b67821272782eaac49caf2aca943ea395446a0","tid":1354023,"uid":13638,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"次次出黎都話玩火<br />\n次次都冇人放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb3a8b8d8e5106c28abe549d6e8eb7565373765","tid":1354023,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實燒村既意思係唔係一齊帶d香燭冥強去幫佢地祖墳同祠堂燒 祭一祭祖？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過我帶既係連儂紙同林奠特別版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0765abd1f588a9049fb555d84787ef04fda084","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3b67821272782eaac49caf2aca943ea395446a0","tid":1354023,"uid":13638,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"次次出黎都話玩火<br />\n次次都冇人放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c244430aedb6e705e382109f957cbd3a86741cc","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"建議admin del燒村post 免遭口實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957ed795869116d3b9cc361203234979c3560f91","tid":1354023,"uid":224945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:41:38.000Z","msg":"到時又指返個矛頭落我哋啲&quot;暴徒&quot;"},{"pid":"0aaa0982651f2223fa05d30254e60f619622e03c","tid":1354023,"uid":37922,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbe3c35f55e79dd37f160bec4038721f562e022b","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:46:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6605204798c36bf57c58f6ee73e476c068080fa","tid":1354023,"uid":37922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73c98140cef1ce99af82c7867ef90d1323e37e82","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf4b488fc1e21f5074ca8bfe73fedeacbf8660d2","tid":1354023,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"元朗清潔大隊<br />\n<br />\n謹記帶口罩同殺蟲劑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpcMmGa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpcMmGa.png&h=a7507a7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3e5a0adf5260cfb1cc2cdc235b5092e0507fc58","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f43b273edaea835082bd262ef374ecc92a194922","tid":1354023,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"小心三毛正負評數帶動風向"},{"pid":"07086b96bf4eba4f40c1a6c7627f10f0608948d1","tid":1354023,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f83b95f47c0d98bc9922dd75a735d3004f2027","tid":1354023,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"[727光復元朗] 727元朗反黑反恐行動部署提議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354479</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好玩火，係到燒雜物only"},{"pid":"5bc66a804f30a50c7a4e73e3badb6ccafef91768","tid":1354023,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"可以睇下我嘅提議～<br />\n<br />\n727光復元朗 (副題：元朗反黑反恐行動) <br />\n口號：肅清鄉黑，除暴安良 <br />\n目的：以武力震懾元朗鄉黑勢力，保障元朗社區安全。 <br />\n<br />\n727香港人嘅主要目標有 <br />\n1. 針對鄉黑黃賭毒勢力經濟進行破壞 (首要目標：黃色經濟) <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好唔記得除咗元朗有黑社會之外。 <br />\n元朗區同屯門公園一樣，有色情流鶯問題。 <br />\n掃鄉黑圍村個時，幫埋元朗區搞掂埋黃色問題。 <br />\n<br />\n建議： <br />\n進行141洗樓行動，對流鶯進行驅趕。 <br />\n為咗cut班鄉黑嘅收入 <br />\n<br />\n一樓一地址141個網有架啦。我睇下post唔post出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非都可以係一樓一門口貼下紙仔 <br />\n個人推介可以貼五十路林鄭av封面圖同鄭若驊大波圖係一樓一舊樓門口。 <br />\n<br />\n勇武手足可以注意睇下啲粉紅光管，啲門口cam可以點做。<br />\n<br />\n同埋call埋入境處舉報有人違反逗留條件，入境處都有執法嘅權力。 <br />\n<br />\n舉報違反入境條例罪行 <a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Finvestigation%2Fonlinereportoffence.htm&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=13a27013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm</a><br />\n電話：入境事務處24小時舉報熱線： (852) 2824 1551 (舉報後獲提供一個檔案編號) <br />\n<br />\n人地已經ready <br />\n［遍地開花］年輕紀律部隊要爬山 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n麻雀館大家睇下可以點搞，我唔熟<br />\n<br />\n地形分析：<br />\n【光復元朗】作為一個元朗居民我有啲野想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351965</a><br />\n我係一個由細到大都係圍村長大嘅港女，我有講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354569/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354569/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"48933b582ea4331e14c93d515185570efbb760c7","tid":1354023,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"光覆香港"},{"pid":"1abca0876a538d447708f9b84a9df777951f8dcd","tid":1354023,"uid":283226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26b510c5462497f5fb3d3d92f7502f6920225d09","tid":1354023,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"建議admin del燒村post 免遭口實"}]}